@{U}Welcome to Laplace V0.13@{UU}

   To install Laplace simply start the installer script by double clicking  on
'Install'. This script requires the @{"Installer" LINK "Installer"} V43.3 or better. You can find it
in the AMINET, look out for @{B}util/misc/Installer43_3.lha@{UB}

   Before you try to install Laplace, you should be sure, that your @{"system" LINK "RequirementsENG"}  is
able to run Laplace.

   Additionally you  require MUI  V3.2 or  better,  you find  it also  in  the
AMINET: @{B}util/libs/muiXXusr.lha@{UB}, where XX is the version number (38 is the lat-
est).

